channel.title: Which Source?
channel.description:
Hey, I'm looking for a good source to base my senior exit project on. Any good ideas? and I mean a really decent server.
I would love to use the rsd2v frame work but I have no clue where to start can someone point me in the right direction?

item.title: Which Source?
item.dc:creator: @Mr_Mopar1 Mr Mopar
item.description:
@Mr_Mopar1 wrote:

[quote=“pkpoison, post:2, topic:326894”]Depends, if you want a shitty server thats pretty much done download DeltaScape.

If you want a blank server then download Shards Revolutions which is very stable.

If you need help add me on msn, xskaterx1165@aol.com[/quote]
Deltascape isn’t “shitty” You might think “there’s too many bugs” or “shit pking”
You can clean it out.
But if anything, deltascape OR devo.
